Package siminov.orm.parsers


Class Summary
AnnotationParser Exposes methods to parse annotation defined in POJO class.
ApplicationDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Application Descriptor information as per define in ApplicationDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
DatabaseDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Database Descriptor information as per define in DatabaseDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
DatabaseMappingDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Library Descriptor information as per define in DatabaseDescriptor.si.xml or LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
LibraryDescriptorParser Exposes methods to parse Library Descriptor information as per define in LibraryDescriptor.si.xml file by application.
QuickDatabaseMappingDescriptorParser Exposes methods to quickly parse database mapping descriptor defined by application.
SiminovSAXDefaultHandler Exposes common methods which are required by every SIMINOV parsers.
